OL,3,CHorse collapses and dies following
OL,4,CGold Cup race at Cheltenham Festival
OL,6,FA third horse has died at the
OL,7,FCheltenham Festival after running in
OL,8,Fthe Gold Cup.
OL,10,FEnvoi Allen was due to retire
OL,11,Ffollowing his ninth-place run in the
OL,12,Fblue riband event. It was his eighth
OL,13,Fappearance at the Festival.
OL,15,FDuring his career he won 10 Grade One
OL,16,Fraces, having started out with trainer
OL,17,FGordon Elliott before moving to Henry
OL,18,Fde Bromhead.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
