CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773446586
OL,3,CHorse collapses and dies following
OL,4,CGold Cup race at Cheltenham Festival
OL,6,FHe most recently became the first
OL,7,Fhorse to win the Down Royal Champion
OL,8,FChase on three occasions.
OL,10,FRichard Thompson, director of the
OL,11,FNewmarket-based Cheveley Park Stud,
OL,12,Fwho owned Envoi Allen, said: "We
OL,13,Fdidn't see it. The vets OK-ed them all
OL,14,F(after the race) and Darragh
OL,15,F(O'Keeffe, jockey) said he was
OL,16,Fpricking his ears, then he came up and
OL,17,Fwent over as he was coming out of the
OL,18,Fchute.
OL,20,F"He had just retired, and he's just
OL,21,Fgone in a minute or two.
OL,26,@tD@^OU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
