FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773446586
OL,3,CHorse collapses and dies following
OL,4,CGold Cup race at Cheltenham Festival
OL,6,F"He's finished the race, the vets have
OL,7,Fhad a look, he's walked on, and he's
OL,8,Fgone down before the chute."
OL,10,FEnvoi Allen had won three times at the
OL,11,FFestival, landing the 2019 Champion
OL,12,FBumper, the 2020 Ballymore Novices'
OL,13,FHurdle, now known as the Turners, and
OL,14,Fthe 2023 Ryanair Chase, as well as
OL,15,Fplacing on a further three occasions.
OL,17,FThompson added: "He was such an
OL,18,Funbelievable horse. This was not the
OL,19,Fending we wanted, but unfortunately,
OL,20,Fthat is what has happened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@\O]yD@QOU
