OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773446586
OL,3,CHorse collapses and dies following
OL,4,CGold Cup race at Cheltenham Festival
OL,6,F"He's been an incredible servant,
OL,7,Fwonderful over the years, and this is
OL,8,Fsuch a sad way to go.
OL,10,F"He's gone doing what he loves; he
OL,11,Fjust retired at that moment. It's a
OL,12,Ftough one."
